WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:13.440
I can tell you

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:15.640
that all the ports

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:17.440
have been blocked by the police.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.000
You can't escape.

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:19.860
Really?

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:23.360
If I take you as a hostage,

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:26.370
I can force them to clear a path.

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:30.320
You broke my heart.

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:32.960
Look at your feet.

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:42.330
You did this?

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:43.480
Yes.

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:45.040
To catch me,

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:47.480
you bet your own life.

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:48.480
To you,

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:49.410
this is a gamble.

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:51.760
But it's not to me.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.960
I could have killed you all at the chemical plant,

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:55.840
but I didn't.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:57.280
Why do you keep pushing,

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:58.360
refusing to let me go?

00:00:58.360 --> 00:00:58.960
Aunt Rong.

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:00.280
Don't forget,

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:01.120
just tonight,

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:03.600
you set a trap at Haifeng Company

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:04.239
to kill me.

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:08.539
That was to teach you a lesson,

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.210
to make you stop obsessing.

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:15.810
I am not like you.

00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:20.160
I won't let myself be blinded by hatred.

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:22.160
The reason I do this

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:24.440
is because of my duty.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:27.400
Duty?

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:30.400
Do you know

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:32.720
if this boat sinks in a while,

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:33.880
we will all die here?

00:01:35.160 --> 00:01:36.090
Of course I know.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.460
But if I let you escape,

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:41.200
more people will die because of you.

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.520
I'd rather die with you

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:44.400
than let you get away.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:48.039
What goes around comes around.

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:50.120
Do you know

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:52.620
that the way you are now

00:01:54.360 --> 00:01:56.490
is exactly like your father back then?

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.400
If he had let me go back then,

00:01:58.520 --> 00:01:59.800
I wouldn't have pushed him down.

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:02.000
You don't deserve to mention my father.

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:05.560
What my father didn't finish back then,

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:06.520
I will continue.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:08.280
But you

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:10.720
must face the justice of the law.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.580
Then I'll die here.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:16.640
Dying here

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.600
is better than facing your so-called justice.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:29.940
Your analysis is correct.

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:34.960
I did filter targets on the 'Listen to Her' app.

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:39.600
Besides the few cases already carried out,

00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:42.329
I made perfect revenge plans for 68 other people.

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:44.840
Even if I die,

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:47.160
the rest of these people

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:48.820
will continue their revenge.

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:56.370
We will do our best to stop crimes from happening.

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.000
Even if we can't,

00:02:58.600 --> 00:03:01.440
we will bring all criminals to justice.

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:26.480
Chen.

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:31.079
Compared to your dad,

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:34.880
you have outdone him.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.410
But it's such a pity.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.200
None of you want to join the Scavengers.

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:51.560
I am very curious.

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.340
When did you start suspecting me?

00:03:55.720 --> 00:03:56.320
After all.

00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:57.840
After all, you hid so well.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:04.340
During the Wangwu Village dismemberment case,

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:06.850
I had already started suspecting you.

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:08.120
We investigated

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:10.650
the two skeletons dug out from Qingshazhang.

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:13.740
Tests showed that one of the girls

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:16.079
was an orphan.

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:22.450
She grew up in Jiangcheng Welfare Institute.

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:24.850
After she got into college,

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.970
someone sponsored her regularly.

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:30.440
And that sponsor

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:32.420
was you.

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:38.840
That child was very good.

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.380
She was very grateful.

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:47.260
She would always call to greet me.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:51.740
So when I lost contact with her for three months,

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:52.720
I realized

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:54.890
she had an accident.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:59.050
I tried everything to investigate her whereabouts.

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.130
Later, her roommate told me

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:03.600
she went to a place called

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:04.720
Wangwu Village.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.360
I didn't find her there,

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.080
but I met

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.490
Li Zhaodi, who escaped,

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:13.320
who later became Lin Xiaoai.

00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:16.480
Help me.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:22.460
At first I thought it was just a coincidence.

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:26.480
Because you sponsored more than one orphan and poor student,

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:29.280
and you also cared deeply for Zhao Wen's daughter.

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:31.920
Until that day we went to eat.

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:34.120
Qingqing.

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:35.200
What do you want to eat?

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:36.260
I'll order for you.

00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:37.720
I want a large bowl of ramen.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:38.400
With extra noodles,

00:05:38.400 --> 00:05:39.930
extra meat, and extra soup.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.440
Isn't that two portions?

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:42.290
One portion.

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:43.680
Excuse me.

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:45.140
Two bowls of ramen.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:45.490
Okay.

00:05:46.159 --> 00:05:46.420
Hey.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:48.480
Did you finish your homework today?

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:49.000
Yes, I did.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:49.600
Let me see.

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:02.600
So based on these two small details,

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:06.130
you suspect there's something wrong with me?

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:08.810
I visited the orphanage you stayed at,

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:11.210
high school,

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.330
university,

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:16.700
and learned everything about your past.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:19.680
In these cases,

00:06:21.080 --> 00:06:24.280
someone has been manipulating things behind the scenes.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.930
So we concluded that

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:28.120
the mastermind behind it

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:32.210
is highly likely to have similar experiences as the killer.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.020
They are exactly the same.

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:37.000
Qiu Chen talked to Master,

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.730
and asked just like Master did.

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:40.120
I will definitely investigate

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.760
until the truth comes to light.

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:43.020
When I first saved you,

00:06:43.640 --> 00:06:45.100
I had a question in my mind.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:49.920
Why did Master sacrifice himself investigating the Scavenger,

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:50.520
while you,

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:52.800
kidnapped by the Scavenger for so long,

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:54.760
came out completely unscathed?

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:56.560
I have always suspected that you

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:59.090
reached some kind of deal with the Scavenger.

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:04.810
Locard's exchange principle told me,

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:07.280
every contact

00:07:08.760 --> 00:07:09.620
leaves a trace.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.940
You boast yourself as a trace scavenger,

00:07:16.320 --> 00:07:18.760
helping killers commit crimes time after time,

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:20.490
and then erasing their tracks.

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:23.860
But what you don't know is,

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:27.120
no matter how much time passes,

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:29.050
no matter how hidden the method is,

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:31.400
traces will definitely be left behind.

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:37.420
Because there is no such thing as a perfect crime in this world.

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:45.880
I've completely lost to you,

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:46.680
Xiaochen.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:51.280
No.

00:07:53.200 --> 00:07:54.400
You didn't lose to me.

00:07:55.880 --> 00:07:57.010
You lost to justice.

00:08:10.520 --> 00:08:11.120
Gu Yuming,

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:14.370
I want to ask you one last question.

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:16.650
Go ahead.

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:28.760
I gave so much for Mr. Qiu,

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:32.900
was he really never moved?

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:35.080
Mr. Qiu.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:35.400
Oh.

00:08:35.559 --> 00:08:36.490
Why are you here?

00:08:54.520 --> 00:08:55.450
Do you remember?

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:57.880
One day it was raining heavily,

00:08:57.880 --> 00:08:59.280
you brought him wontons,

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.040
he didn't eat them

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:02.300
and told you to go back,

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:04.080
and you were very sad.

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:06.940
I asked him afterwards

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:08.810
why he couldn't accept you.

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:11.210
Do you know what he said?

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:22.160
Watching a movie.

00:09:22.680 --> 00:09:23.140
Master.

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:28.840
Mr. Qiu.

00:09:30.400 --> 00:09:31.330
Why are you here?

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.360
I was afraid you hadn't eaten,

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:34.820
so I made you some wontons.

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:38.420
An Rong,

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:40.800
I understand your feelings,

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.600
but you should go back first.

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.280
Don't come here anymore.

00:09:46.280 --> 00:09:47.400
I don't have time to eat.

00:09:47.400 --> 00:09:47.720
Ah.

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:49.360
But I...

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:50.100
Mr. Qiu.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:50.780
Master.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.080
If you have something else to do,

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:54.560
we can watch it another day.

00:09:54.560 --> 00:09:55.920
It's raining pretty heavily.

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:57.240
It's fine. We agreed to watch a movie.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.040
Wait a moment.

00:09:58.520 --> 00:09:58.760
Ah.

00:09:59.240 --> 00:09:59.840
Wait here.

00:10:02.280 --> 00:10:02.760
Mr. Qiu,

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:06.520
you have time to watch a movie with them,

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:09.880
but no time to eat the wontons I made for you?

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:17.260
An Rong.

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:24.020
An Rong.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:25.760
I want to tell you,

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:27.920
you and me,

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.620
it's absolutely impossible.

00:10:31.520 --> 00:10:33.050
Don't waste your time on me.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.060
Do you understand?

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:43.800
An Rong.

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:54.040
Old Qiu,

00:10:54.560 --> 00:10:55.720
you hurt that girl.

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:56.760
That's not good.

00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:57.490
Yeah, you are

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:58.520
too cruel.

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:02.520
What should I

00:11:02.520 --> 00:11:03.320
do about this?

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:06.770
If I am not cruel now,

00:11:07.040 --> 00:11:08.640
I will hurt her in the future.

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:09.640
Look at my age.

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:10.480
And I have a kid.

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:11.080
As for her,

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:11.980
she is so young.

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:13.160
She has a long life ahead of her.

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.090
Deserve better.

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:14.640
What do you know?

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:15.170
You know.

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:17.730
Let's just leave it at that.

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:20.400
He said you were still young.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:22.610
You had a long road ahead of you.

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:26.130
He didn't want to hold you back.

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:36.600
You just said that child was grateful.

00:11:44.280 --> 00:11:47.640
Master was thinking of how to protect you right until he died.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:49.700
Yet you refused to come to your senses

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:52.250
and killed him with your own hands.

00:11:56.120 --> 00:11:56.450
What?

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:00.520
Protect me?

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:10.360
Hahaha.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:12.640
You're lying!

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:15.520
You're all lying!

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:19.620
What he was protecting

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:21.400
was the rigid law

00:12:22.840 --> 00:12:24.600
and his ridiculous pride.

00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:28.120
You are all lying.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:32.700
How could he possibly protect me?

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.450
He accepted you a long time ago.

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:42.480
Just

00:12:44.600 --> 00:12:46.080
not in the way you wanted.

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:53.280
My dad and I

00:12:55.040 --> 00:12:57.370
have treated you as family for a long time.

00:12:57.720 --> 00:12:58.480
Aww.

00:12:58.560 --> 00:12:59.560
Come here, Chenchen.

00:12:59.560 --> 00:13:00.240
Dad.

00:13:00.400 --> 00:13:01.120
Haha.

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:01.980
Did you miss me?

00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:02.520
Yes.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:04.200
I did. Ouch.

00:13:04.280 --> 00:13:04.920
Let me ask you,

00:13:04.920 --> 00:13:05.400
how much did you miss me?

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:05.840
Mhm.

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:08.720
Hahaha.

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:09.380
An Rong,

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:10.090
thank you

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:11.440
for taking care of Chenchen.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.040
It's nothing.

00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:12.800
Go on in.

00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:15.240
Aww.

00:13:15.240 --> 00:13:15.840
Oh my.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.120
Were you a good boy today?

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:17.720
Yes, I was.

00:13:18.040 --> 00:13:22.120
Happy birthday to you.

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:22.880
Hahaha.

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:24.210
Happy birthday.

00:13:25.000 --> 00:13:25.600
Chenchen,

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:26.780
make a wish.

00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:31.040
I wish

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:35.600
I could always be with Dad and Aunt Rong.

00:13:47.880 --> 00:13:50.010
The one you are least willing to accept

00:13:50.920 --> 00:13:51.720
is yourself.

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:25.280
An Rong is sentenced to death for intentional homicide and deprived of political rights for life.

00:14:59.680 --> 00:14:59.960
Dad.

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:03.860
The scavenger case is solved.

00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:06.480
Don't worry anymore.

00:15:07.520 --> 00:15:08.320
In the future,

00:15:10.360 --> 00:15:11.620
I will live a good life.

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:42.820
Here we are.

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:43.360
Hey!

00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:44.440
Surprise!

00:15:44.680 --> 00:15:45.000
You are here.

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:46.320
Come on, step inside.

00:15:46.320 --> 00:15:47.050
Brother Qiu.

00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:49.200
Come on in.

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:49.720
Hey.

00:15:50.320 --> 00:15:51.280
Hahaha.

00:15:51.280 --> 00:15:52.520
You poked me in the nose.

00:15:52.520 --> 00:15:53.440
Oh, no problem.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:54.640
I mean,

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:55.960
you guys didn't have to

00:15:55.960 --> 00:15:57.160
bring so many things.

00:15:57.160 --> 00:15:58.240
My master said

00:15:58.240 --> 00:15:59.200
this place is too plain.

00:15:59.200 --> 00:16:00.120
You need some style.

00:16:00.120 --> 00:16:01.980
Otherwise you'll get depressed.

00:16:02.280 --> 00:16:03.480
I have the most style.

00:16:03.480 --> 00:16:03.940
Come on.

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:04.560
Qingqing,

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:05.760
take a picture for us.

00:16:06.040 --> 00:16:06.320
Come on.

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:06.980
Captain Gu.

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:09.520
Come here.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:15.200
By the way,

00:16:15.200 --> 00:16:15.930
Brother Qiu,

00:16:16.280 --> 00:16:17.610
where did Teacher An go?

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:18.960
I miss her.

00:16:22.520 --> 00:16:23.180
Teacher An?

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:25.360
Teacher An

00:16:25.680 --> 00:16:26.410
went abroad.

00:16:26.880 --> 00:16:28.680
You will see her when you grow up.

00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:30.080
Okay.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:38.680
Let me see.

00:16:38.920 --> 00:16:39.840
Thank you.

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:42.380
Oh, not bad.

00:16:42.920 --> 00:16:43.580
Looks good.

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:45.080
Hey.

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:47.880
Hahaha.

00:16:47.880 --> 00:16:48.880
Look at how I look.

00:16:49.720 --> 00:16:50.250
Qiu Chen.

00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:52.160
You've rested enough.

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:53.890
It's time to return to the team.

00:16:54.080 --> 00:16:54.400
Oh.

00:16:55.240 --> 00:16:55.440
Ah.

00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:56.680
Then,

00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:57.640
Sixty-eight people.

00:16:57.640 --> 00:16:58.720
Have you found them?

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:00.560
Sixty-eight people are lining up waiting for you.

00:17:00.560 --> 00:17:00.920
Yeah.

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:02.720
Lining up waiting for me.

00:17:03.400 --> 00:17:04.000
Then

00:17:04.000 --> 00:17:04.720
let them

00:17:05.119 --> 00:17:06.079
wait a little longer.

00:17:06.079 --> 00:17:07.440
I'll rest for a few more days.

00:17:07.440 --> 00:17:07.800
No.

00:17:09.200 --> 00:17:10.260
Stop imitating me.

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:12.849
It's time for lunch.

00:17:13.160 --> 00:17:14.079
Let's go eat.

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:15.240
Brother Chen.

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:16.300
Let's go together.

00:17:19.319 --> 00:17:19.680
Are you not hungry?

00:17:19.680 --> 00:17:20.280
Uh.

00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:21.210
Then we won't

00:17:21.359 --> 00:17:22.760
bother Qiu Chen anymore.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:25.839
Near my house,

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:28.400
there's a newly opened

00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:29.530
hot pot restaurant.

00:17:30.120 --> 00:17:30.980
It tastes okay.

00:17:33.680 --> 00:17:34.440
This guy

00:17:34.800 --> 00:17:36.260
wants to treat us to a meal.

00:17:38.040 --> 00:17:39.500
I only said it tastes fine.

00:17:39.640 --> 00:17:40.800
I didn't say it's my treat.

00:17:40.800 --> 00:17:41.120
Hey, hey, hey.

00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:41.720
Go, go, go.

00:17:41.800 --> 00:17:43.000
Did you get the money?

00:17:44.200 --> 00:17:44.930
Is this real?

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:45.760
Pinch me.

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:47.720
Hurry up, say less and go.